d in Glasgow, will be confident in winning a small group sprint against nearly anyone except the dominant sprinter Wiebes, for whom she has spent a lot of 2024 doing lead-outs for at SD Worx.\", \"from\": 4955, \"to\": 5291, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5022, \"end\": 5027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.550351108502638e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 5105, \"end\": 5112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"score\": 0.9999783626311782, \"rank\": 2.16378357999345e-05, \"text\": \"Glasgow\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\"}, {\"begin\": 5283, \"end\": 5290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SD_Worx\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"SD Worx\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SD_Worx\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SD_Worx\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Classics-style\", \"from\": 4958, \"to\": 4976}, {\"ngram\": \"the Pont D'lena finish\", \"from\": 5032, \"to\": 5054}, {\"ngram\": \"Kopecky\", \"from\": 5056, \"to\": 5063}, {\"ngram\": \"solo\", \"from\": 5086, \"to\": 5090}, {\"ngram\": \"a small group sprint\", \"from\": 5143, \"to\": 5163}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly anyone\", \"from\": 5172, \"to\": 5185}, {\"ngram\": \"the dominant sprinter Wiebes\", \"from\": 5193, \"to\": 5221}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 5246, \"to\": 5251}, {\"ngram\": \"lead-outs\", \"from\": 5266, \"to\": 5275}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A course that, especially in the final, is tailor-made for her,\\\" is how Belgium women's road team coach Ludwig Willems described it toHLN.\", \"from\": 5293, \"to\": 5432, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5366, \"end\": 5373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.9999996623046743, \"rank\": 3.3769477692336863e-07, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}, {\"begin\": 5398, \"end\": 5412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ludwig_Willems\", \"score\": 0.9999898967563394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ludwig Willems\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ludwig_Willems\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ludwig_Willems\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A course\", \"from\": 5294, \"to\": 5302}, {\"ngram\": \"toHLN\", \"from\": 5426, \"to\": 5431}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But of course, there are others like that.\", \"from\": 5433, \"to\": 5476, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 5441, \"to\": 5447}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 5459, \"to\": 5465}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lotte [Kopecky] needs a selective race that is made hard early and causes fatigue to creep into the peloton before we reach Paris again.\", \"from\": 5477, \"to\": 5613, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5601, \"end\": 5606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.550351108502638e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lotte\", \"from\": 5477, \"to\": 5482}, {\"ngram\": \"Kopecky\", \"from\": 5484, \"to\": 5491}, {\"ngram\": \"a selective race\", \"from\": 5499, \"to\": 5515}, {\"ngram\": \"fatigue\", \"from\": 5551, \"to\": 5558}, {\"ngram\": \"the peloton\", \"from\": 5573, \"to\": 5584}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Hopefully, we will find a number of allies in that tactic.\", \"from\": 5615, \"to\": 5674, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 5640, \"to\": 5648}, {\"ngram\": \"allies\", \"from\